              "correct_choice": "B",
              "rationale": "Buzz saw Earth as beautiful and precious. A message about caring for Earth connects to his feelings and the story's theme.",
              "text_evidence": "I could see Earth, our home, in the sky overhead-blue water, white clouds, and brown land. I could see the continents, and I knew that they were younger than the Moon dust in which Neil and I were now leaving our footprints.",
