              "read_aloud": "Excerpt. He believes that ‘the next monumental achievement of humanity will be the first landing by an Earthling, a human being, on the planet Mars.’ What is Buzz Aldrin’s opinion about the future? A. Humans should not go to other planets. B. Landing on Mars will be a great achievement. C. The Moon is the only place humans can go. D. Mars is too dangerous for humans to visit.",
